scheduled_maintenances.name: [GLOBAL][Bare Metal Cloud] - End of Installation date change for Proxmox Virtual Environment (VE) 8 and Proxmox Backup Server (BS) 3

incident_updates.body: Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, we are changing the scheduled End of Installation date for Proxmox VE 8 and Proxmox BS 3 at OVHcloud. These OSes were previously scheduled to be available for installation until July 2028. This date has now been changed to August 2026 in accordance with the publisher's official support policy for Proxmox Virtual Environment and Proxmox Backup Server. Please note that this change will only affect future OS installations. Customers who have already installed one of these OSes are not affected by this change. Start time: 26/08/2025 16:00 UTC End time: 02/09/2025 16:00 UTC Service impact: None Thank you for your understanding.
